# Day 17 – Web Scraper to CSV

## What it does
Scrapes the top 10 headlines from Times of India 
and saves them to a structured CSV file.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3
- requests
- BeautifulSoup4
- csv (built-in)

## How to run
pip install requests beautifulsoup4
python toi.py

## Output
Generates headlines.csv with columns: number, headline
